/!\ WIP
{{https://launchpadlibrarian.net/32738622/64.png}}

Add your submissions here. This page will constantly change. 
* Kindly include a preview[48px png] and SVG of all the sizes 16 , 22 , 24 , 32 , 48 px icons as a single compressed archive file .
* For panel[symbolic] icons a preview of the 24px would be sufficient.
* Subscribe to the wiki page to be notified whether the icon was included or not in the theme.

Do note: 
* Submitting the icons here does not mean that it would be automatically included in the theme.
* If we do use the icon , we might include the icon as submitted or edit the icon to fit the theme better.
* Since icons in elementary and humanity have now been merged closer, the icon may be included in elementary-icon-theme too.
